data.description: This beautiful, large 4 bedroom home is ready for you! On the main level, a very large, open family room, kitchen, a breakfast nook and formal dining, great for entertaining the whole crew. All rooms have very tall ceilings, the basement has tall ceilings too! All bedrooms are upstairs with the laundry and full bathroom. All kitchen appliances stay with the home as well as Ring camera system. Fenced back yard with shed.
